{"tid":89894,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"休班警偷拍16歲少女裙底   旺角港鐵站被捕","createTime":"2017-01-21T16:12:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-22T01:14:59.000Z","uid":62257,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a977beaddf7df87044782219bdf12dece6536387","tid":89894,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T16:12:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170121/56205775\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170121%2F56205775&d=Jjls0yldg%2BbC47GMtSCu9wT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=032a1234\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170121%2F56205775&h=5d589ac8\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170121/56205775</a><br />\n港鐵旺角站，下午3時許，有警員巡經上址時，在扶手電梯位置發現一名男子正偷拍一名16歲少女的裙底，立即上前以涉嫌公眾地方行為不檢拘捕33歲姓邢男子，帶返警署調查。警方進一步調查發現，涉案疑犯為一名休班警，現正被扣留調查。警方強調警隊非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍和姑息，定必嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。"},{"pid":"780f280192e72a5f255afa5cc6f35e7e25e3a254","tid":89894,"uid":47352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T16:14:13.000Z","msg":"一定係睇得嗰啲片多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7e042a35633e0cb8bad9edd9fd5089df4d4868f","tid":89894,"uid":50413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T16:16:17.000Z","msg":"痴撚線，真係犯罪集團黎"},{"pid":"239c2b12b05fcc92f6f6c783aaf5c49f2ea71a84","tid":89894,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T16:18:32.000Z","msg":"又係休班警"},{"pid":"59981a38e343c279a399a0ab09b6cd72f1ab0031","tid":89894,"uid":20614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T16:22:39.000Z","msg":"休班警+1分"},{"pid":"8b5927c4b66f5fe48ee6d9f8fc4850a2a12d1eac","tid":89894,"uid":64463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T16:24:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\